{"tid":1207384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中環膠囊旅館 SLEEEP 現極需要大量毛巾！！！","createTime":"2019-06-12T06:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T08:06:36.000Z","uid":862,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cd820c0e480a808345cd03aa935a4b8395a9c8a5","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2374177\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2374177&d=Upau0OFRhNBgg6kYd6CVy5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=b7fc4977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2374177</a><br />\n<br />\n開放咗俾大家免費入去沖涼同休息<br />\n而家唔夠毛巾用<br />\n有無人可以搵到大量乾淨毛巾去！"},{"pid":"722ef281ec14593f845834ed02352f9e31a217be","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b9270ec76035b6936963e0d46f16ba71df2571c","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f17ab4291319794cc95d1f8336931bf3c162ae05","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fe668ee062cb65a8be4437f3ee3f75ca4e93d92","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5420c2b834639de5917c0ce4baae9f8fa456da4","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b17b09e6ee0fd288bde77d093c74a969dd63cea8","tid":1207384,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"有人用棍拍野deam beat 既時候唔好劣<br />\n一齊叫同一句口號加士氣避免士氣此消彼長<br />\n有心理學背後原理<br />\n對陣口號可參考港隊打氣口號<br />\n拍拍~拍拍拍~DIE FOR HONG KONG<br />\n<br />\n引用 雞肉大師 巴打:<br />\n要佢哋一齊嘶哮， 進入同一個呼吸節奏 同一個心跳步伐 <br />\n配合戰鼓(你搵個大水樽好撚大嗰啲 求其搵嘢敲佢有節奏嘅)打拍子 就會將一堆散兵游勇聚合成一個群體<br />\n以往慣例邊個大聲公喇叭就死邊個， 二來呢啲設備貴<br />\n但係水樽就可以有好多個 水樽買得起<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家小心雙眼，戴眼罩被人噴油漆就喪失視力，唔戴又會比人插眼<br />\n<br />\n大家亦小心近距離突然由下巴向上大力推有機會導致頸椎受傷 請各位注意安全免生危險<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNAsyHq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNAsyHq.png&h=c26eaddb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5b9139deb11ace4b09c607e15d215b331993a9c","tid":1207384,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:18:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3baa460038088e20094325cc7759a47242eecde8","tid":1207384,"uid":124163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:19:21.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbe8fbf42124bac59134a30f8f5fdb43a197543","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n有無附近番工嘅朋友幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a990ed4126bf280b32af06df56a35c94daec5f02","tid":1207384,"uid":102185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"79095faf657702e1426ce2482b19d35397bd8d80","tid":1207384,"uid":862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:35:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2d183da6ff69f408af51aca47af9aaf374c01f51","tid":1207384,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea77384f90a0d1dc1408c25ea4d54f796a2a3cdc","tid":1207384,"uid":17875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06